    <sem:predicate>http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition</sem:predicate>
    <sem:object xml:lang="eng" datatype="xsd:string">The followers of Satan who will suffer with him in eternity. Sons of perdition include (1) those who followed Satan and were cast out of heaven for rebellion during premortality, and (2) those who were permitted to be born to this world with physical bodies but then served Satan and turned utterly against God. Those in this second group will be resurrected from the dead but will not be redeemed from the second (spiritual) death and cannot dwell in a kingdom of glory ().</sem:object>
